{"tid":875484,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聽天由命定 逆天而行","createTime":"2018-10-25T02:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T02:46:58.000Z","uid":63883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68b74a1d249799549eb7576daddddd5f33b90d02","tid":875484,"uid":63883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"我只係想盡辦法飽覽燈紅酒綠裡嘅色香味<br />\n直至行屍走肉靈魂都獻俾財色酒氣<br />\n直至用煙紙包住嘅年華都開始走味<br />\n係路燈下曾經照遍歡笑嘅土地<br />\n我不禁問自己呢刻你捨得走未<br />\n係你自己要將自己拋棄<br />\n你話過演活自己　定只係每日都對住自己交戲<br />\n<br />\nHomeless<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一種痛叫 隨意<br />\n痛咪痛 死咪死 無咩所謂 <br />\n當人生意義無咗 無咩用 有咩用 都唔關自己事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6125236f5e926b752cf879e5741179470ea91d","tid":875484,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"到最後你都無得揀"},{"pid":"18acd9f3da1684558201e845e195c097939dc285","tid":875484,"uid":63883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc6125236f5e926b752cf879e5741179470ea91d","tid":875484,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"到最後你都無得揀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"啱呀 個天想你死 想你生 你都決定唔lun到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1598e38089003b113bbd58c22758b4455994d3a4","tid":875484,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18acd9f3da1684558201e845e195c097939dc285","tid":875484,"uid":63883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc6125236f5e926b752cf879e5741179470ea91d","tid":875484,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"到最後你都無得揀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"啱呀 個天想你死 想你生 你都決定唔lun到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"隨心所欲 然後 順其自然"},{"pid":"e94b5c120ed2f589685b977d6e38c6